com.navis.framework.portal.query

Interface DomainQuery

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BasicQuery, Bounded, java.lang.Cloneable, DataQuery, ExecutableQuery, MetaFilter, Ordered, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DomainQueryImpl, NullDomainQuery

    public interface DomainQuery
extends DataQuery, MetaFilter, java.lang.Cloneable
    An object-oriented representation of a database query.

      • getDevComment

java.lang.String getDevComment()

        Returns:
        comment as String

      • appendDevComment

        void appendDevComment(@NotNull
                      java.lang.String inDevComment)
        This method sets comment if no comments were set or appends more comment at the end of the comment. The separator is ", " Limit of developer comment size = DEV_COMMENT_SIZE_LIMIT characters. Extra characters will be cut off. This comment may include, but not limited to: business logic, source, expectations, measurements an so on. It should help in investigation of a possible performance problems.
        Parameters:
        inDevComment - developer comment to append

      • prependDevComment

        void prependDevComment(@NotNull
                       java.lang.String inDevComment)
        This method prepends Dev comment. Useful when the comment is important and needs to take precedence
        Parameters:
        inDevComment - developer comment to append
